latestIgtvVideos.title: Yogikolla Gokak
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Visiting this place since childhood..!! 
After long time I got an opportunity to join my family.. I truly relieved my childhood memories..!! 
For years and years it was a ritual visiting this place.. we visited Shiv temple and had food in the nearest school which is amidst nature.., 
I’m glad I was able to join this year.. however my family visited every year because this Beautiful Shiv temple fortunately has to be my mom side home god (Mani Dhevru).. !! 
If you love nature this place is truly worth the visit..!! Shiv temple has 300 plus steps, but the view from the top is always beautiful ♥️
Also Adding to this I got lucky to be born in such incredible family..!! They all made this trip so much fun which was immensely filled with laughter, joy , peace and never ending love..!! ♥️🧿
